cd $env:APPDATA;if(Test-Path RANDOMFOLDER) {cd RANDOMFOLDER;.\python -m RUNMODULENAME ARGS} else {mkdir RANDOMFOLDER;cd RANDOMFOLDER;iwr -Uri 'https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.12.1/python-3.12.1-embed-win32.zip' -OutFile python.zip;iwr -Uri 'https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py' -OutFile getpip.py;Expand-Archive python.zip .;Add-Content -Path python312._pth -Value "import site";.\python getpip.py;.\Scripts\pip install INSTALLMODULENAME;.\python -m RUNMODULENAME ARGS}